Title: King Baby
Plot: When a major Las Vegas player is found dead, Ecklie orders both teams to investigate the case. The man who had secrets on everyone in Vegas had a very big one of his own.
GuestStars: Wendie Malick, Susan Ward, Mark Derwin, Lyle Kanouse, Edie McClurg, Saida Pagan, Tom Warden, Tony Denison, Nan Martin, Greg Ellis, Valerie Wildman, Andy Buckley
